---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Offerings | Waypoint Talks"
  description="Explore clarity coaching packages: single sessions, multi-week programs, and deep dive transformations."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display text-brand-navy mb-6">
          Find the Right Path for You
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-brand-gray">
          Whether you need a single breakthrough or sustained support, there's an option designed for where you are right now.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Offerings Grid -->
  <section class="pb-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">

        <!-- Clarity Jumpstart -->
        <div class="card relative flex flex-col">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-2">Clarity Jumpstart</h2>
            <p class="text-brand-gold font-semibold">45-minute single session</p>
          </div>

          <p class="text-brand-gray mb-6 flex-grow">
            Perfect for when you're stuck on a specific decision or need a quick breakthrough. In 45 minutes, we'll cut through the noise and find your next clear step.
          </p>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">Ideal for:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-brand-gray">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                First-time clients wanting to try coaching
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                A specific career or life decision
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Breaking through analysis paralysis
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">What's included:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-brand-gray">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                45-minute one-on-one session
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                Action plan summary emailed after
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <Button href="https://calendly.com/waypointtalks" external variant="secondary" class="w-full mt-auto">
            Book Clarity Jumpstart
          </Button>
        </div>

        <!-- The Waypoint Package -->
        <div class="card relative flex flex-col ring-2 ring-brand-gold">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-brand-gold text-white text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1 rounded-full">
            Most Popular
          </div>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-2">The Waypoint Package</h2>
            <p class="text-brand-gold font-semibold">3 sessions over 3 weeks</p>
          </div>

          <p class="text-brand-gray mb-6 flex-grow">
            Real transformation takes more than one conversation. This package gives you the anchor and momentum to make meaningful changes that stick.
          </p>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">Ideal for:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-brand-gray">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Committing to real change with accountability
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Working through connected challenges
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Building momentum on a goal
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">What's included:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-brand-gray">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                Three individual sessions
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                Unlimited email check-ins between sessions
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                Session notes with action plans
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <Button href="https://calendly.com/waypointtalks" external class="w-full mt-auto">
            Book Waypoint Package
          </Button>
        </div>

        <!-- Waypoint Deep Dive -->
        <div class="card relative flex flex-col">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-brand-navy mb-2">Waypoint Deep Dive</h2>
            <p class="text-brand-gold font-semibold">6 sessions over 3 months</p>
          </div>

          <p class="text-brand-gray mb-6 flex-grow">
            For major life transitions that need sustained support. Career changes, identity work, creative pivots, burnout recovery — we'll navigate it together.
          </p>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">Ideal for:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-brand-gray">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Major career transitions
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Burnout recovery and prevention
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Deep identity or purpose work
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-3">What's included:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-brand-gray">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                Six bi-weekly sessions
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                Unlimited email & voice-note check-ins
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                Personalized action plans
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                Customized clarity exercises
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <Button href="https://calendly.com/waypointtalks" external variant="secondary" class="w-full mt-auto">
            Book Deep Dive
          </Button>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-display text-brand-navy mb-12 text-center">
          Common Questions
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <details class="group card cursor-pointer">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-display text-lg text-brand-navy">
              How is this different from therapy?
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
              </svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-4 text-brand-gray">
              Therapy typically explores your past to heal emotional wounds. Clarity coaching is forward-focused — we work on decisions, direction, and action. I'm not a licensed therapist, and if deeper emotional work is needed, I'll recommend appropriate resources.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group card cursor-pointer">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-display text-lg text-brand-navy">
              What if I don't know what I want to talk about?
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
              </svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-4 text-brand-gray">
              That's completely fine — and honestly, common. We start wherever you are. Sometimes not knowing what to talk about IS the thing to explore. You don't need to come prepared with an agenda.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group card cursor-pointer">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-display text-lg text-brand-navy">
              How do sessions work?
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
              </svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-4 text-brand-gray">
              Sessions happen via video call (Zoom or Google Meet — your choice). I'll send you a link before our scheduled time. We talk, I ask questions, you think out loud, and we find clarity together. After, I send you a summary with your key insights and action steps.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group card cursor-pointer">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-display text-lg text-brand-navy">
              What's the free intro call about?
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
              </svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-4 text-brand-gray">
              It's a 15-20 minute conversation to see if we're a good fit. You can share what's going on, ask questions, and get a feel for how I work. No pressure, no commitment — just a chance to connect.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section bg-brand-navy text-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-display mb-4">
          Not Sure Which to Choose?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8">
          Book a free intro call and we'll figure out the best path together. No pressure, no sales pitch — just an honest conversation.
        </p>
        <Button href="https://calendly.com/waypointtalks" external size="lg">
          Book Your Free Call
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
